== Overview ==

The '''[[Talsian Warfront]]''' (commonly called '''Talsia''' or '''Tals''') is the second major outland zone in Cybots — a vast, active military theatre where Controllers fight alongside [[CyCorps]] and the [[Legionnaires]] against the Federate military. It is significantly more demanding than [[Vulcore Plain|Vulcore]], both in combat intensity and strategic depth. Unlike Vulcore's open wasteland, Talsia is a structured battlefield with defined sectors, warships, heavily armed tank columns, fortified installations, and elite enemy units.

This guide covers the full progression arc from your first patrol in Delta Sector through to the endgame beyond 18,000 [[Talsian Rank Points|TRP]].

