=== Technology Checklist ===
These should ideally be completed before entering Talsia:
* [[Magmatic Technology]] — [[Magmatic]] reactor on [[CySentinel]] is critical
* [[Bulwark Technology]] — for [[Bulwark]] Chassis (optional)

=== Coming from Vulcore ===
At the end of [[Vulcore Plain|Vulcore]] Patrol 6 (the pre-Talsia patrol), your squad should look roughly like:
* 1× [[Reaper]] (Level 12+) — equipped with [[Syphonic Immobilizer|Immobilizer]] + [[Pulse Streamer]]
* 1× [[Bulwark]] (Level 10+) — primary attacker (optional)
* 4× [[Seer|Seers]] (Level 10) — the engine of your squad's deflection, fire rate, and support
* 1× [[CySentinel]] (Level 12–16) — shielding and protection
* 1× [[Crusader]] (Level 10–12) — primary heavy attacker (2 Crusaders are optional)

If you're unsure whether you're ready for Talsia, see the [[Vulcore Guide]] for the full pre-Talsia preparation.

