==== Phase 1 Strategy ====
[[File:Fedbasedead1.jpg|thumb|right|220px|A destroyed Federate position — the spoils of a successful patrol.]]

'''Mission priority in Delta:'''
# '''Bombardier (Disrupt Bombing Runs)''' — Best Delta mission. Lots of Accolades and TRP. Kill the Grenadier first turn; the [[Reaper]] drains the Shield Projector; then all kill the Lieutenant second turn.
# '''Tank Threat''' — Use the orbital drain satellite (0.9 shots/turn, drains 10,000). Kill Battle Tanks first (fire second turn with heavy weapons), then Main Battle Tanks (600 armour damage second turn), then Cruiser Tanks (900 armour damage but only 1k reactor — drain with Reaper [[Magnatron]]).
# '''Freighter Escort''' — Decent; defend the freighter. If storm troopers have 2 Lieutenants, kill Lieutenants first.
# '''Priority Defence''' — Good for TRP/Accolades + experience ×2 bonus.
# '''Sector Patrol''' — Easiest. Just keep walking until you get back to base.

'''Between missions:'''
* Attack '''Bunkers''' (3 Accolades each — easy)
* Attack '''Tank Squads''' when encountered as mission objectives
* Attack '''Destroyers''' (+25 TRP +15 Accolades — worth doing)
* Avoid '''Fire Bases''' if they have shields and Sabretooth turrets — the cannon can kill units
* Skip standard infantry patrols (no Accolades, wastes KC)

'''Leave Delta when you have:'''
* 800 TRP (Order of Merit unlocked — grants 500 Accolades)
* 2,250 Accolades spare to buy [[Plasma Technology]]
* [[CySentinel]] at Level 13+ (Level 16 optimal for Alpha; if less than Level 16 you need 1.6M+ cash)
* If below Level 16 CySentinel: use the [[Bulwark]] / Seer team, add 4 Seers and [[Plasma Turbo-Cannon]] on [[Crusader]], use Magnetic Actuators for 25% fire rate — get to Level 16 CySentinel and 2.5M cash before Alpha.

