=== Phase 5 — Endgame (18,000 TRP Cap) ===
[[File:Raven-blue.png|thumb|right|220px|[[Raven]] — unlocked at 18,000 TRP.]]

At '''18,000 TRP''', the MRP conversion rate reaches its maximum (~7,500 XP per MRP at max BM). No additional TRP increases XP/credit output from missions.

This means: '''you can now abort unwanted missions''' (costs −50 TRP and Accolades) without significant loss. You are now farming '''experience and credits''' rather than TRP.

At this point, your squad should also be ready for '''[[Gamma Sector]]'''

Also at 18,000 TRP: the '''[[Raven]]''' chassis is unlocked.

