==== Endgame Mission Strategy ====
At 18k+ TRP:
* '''[[#Mining Facility Raid|Mining Facility Raid]]''' and '''[[#Blockade|Blockade]]''' become the best missions — highest MRP yield = 2M+ XP per mission
* '''Chassis Recovery''' and '''Reinforce Besieged Base''' → abort (recover + abort; don't exit and re-enter patrol — wastes KC)
* You can now attack everything encountered — 1–2 KC per battle at high BM
* TRAFs are no longer necessary for TRP; they can be risky for bots
* Battle Cruisers are now easy — all-attack the Battle Cruiser hull for a quick kill

