== Mission Guide ==
Missions are accepted at the Mission Briefing in Delta or Alpha Sector. Completing a mission converts all accumulated [[Mission Reward Points|MRP]] into experience and credits at a rate determined by your TRP and BM.

=== Understanding MRP Conversion ===
* '''TRP''' — Higher TRP = more XP per MRP (caps at 18,000 TRP)
* '''BM (Battle Merit)''' — Higher BM = more XP per MRP (caps at ~14,000,000 BM)
* At maximum TRP (18k) and high BM (~30M+), a single mission can yield '''1–2 million XP''' and '''$1–2M credits'''
* The faster you build TRP early, the more XP each patrol earns overall

