== Technology Purchase Order ==
[[File:Obliterator.jpg|thumb|right|220px|[[Obliterator]] — 1,000 Accolades each; buy multiple at endgame.]]

The recommended technology and equipment purchase order is:

# '''[[Plasma Technology]]''' (2,250 Accolades) — Buy as soon as you have 800 TRP and 2,250 spare Accolades. Plasma weapons ([[Plasma Turbo-Cannon]], [[Plasma Anamorph]] shields) are the foundation of Alpha Sector. Do not delay.
# '''1–2 [[Obliterator|Obliterators]]''' (1,000 Accolades each) — Buy after Plasma Tech. Equip on [[Crusader]]. The [[Obliterator]]'s high crit rate also helps break [[Reinforced Wall|Reinforced Wall]] deflection in TRAFs.
# '''[[Storm Weapons Technology]]''' (2,250 Accolades) — Buy after Plasma Tech and 1–2 Obliterators. Unlocks [[Storm Bringer]] and [[Hail Bringer]] for [[Bulwark]] and [[Leviathan]].

